Courtesy #DStv403 #eNCA  JOHANNESBURG - Action Society’s Ian Cameron says Police Minister Bheki Cele has exposed himself as someone who has lost touch with people and the issues they face. Cameron has laid several charges against Cele. READ: Cameron to take legal action against Cele The minister shouted at Cameron after he questioned his ability to protect citizens during a meeting with Gugulethu residents earlier this week. Cameron was then dragged out of the venue by police officers.